description:
Oiseau`s Noctowl is Oiseau partner who watches Pokémon Sky Relay`s with him. Bonnie noted that Oiseau`s Noctowl looked like Oiseau. Unfortunately it cannot participate in the relay`s as Oiseau does not have enough flying Pokémon to make a team.
None of its moves were revealed in the episode.
name: Yorunozuku (Oiseau)
